OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775239864
OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of helping
OL,4,Corganised crime group smuggle people
OL,6,FA 25-year-old woman has been arrested
OL,7,Fin Wrexham after it has been alleged
OL,8,Fshe laundered money for a people
OL,9,Fsmuggling organised crime group.
OL,11,FThe National Crime Agency arrested
OL,12,Fthree people as part of the
OL,13,Fcoordinated action with French police
OL,14,Finto the group involved in
OL,15,Ftransporting Vietnamese migrants to
OL,16,Fthe UK in lorries and small boats.
OL,18,FOfficers apprehended the woman at an
OL,19,Faddress in Wrexham and a 25-year-old
OL,20,Fman in Newcastle-upon-Tyne on 30 March.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
