FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775239864
OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of helping
OL,4,Corganised crime group smuggle people
OL,6,FThe woman is suspected of assisting
OL,7,Fthe group by laundering money, while
OL,8,Fthe man is believed to have organised
OL,9,Ffacilitation through lower members of
OL,10,Fthe crime group.
OL,12,FSpecialist officers from the NCA's
OL,13,FNational Extradition Unit also
OL,14,Fapprehended a 26-year-old man in
OL,15,FBirmingham after a warrant for his
OL,16,Farrest was issued by French
OL,17,Fauthorities. He is suspected of
OL,18,Foverseeing accommodation for migrants
OL,19,Fdestined for the UK.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
