OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775239864
OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of helping
OL,4,Corganised crime group smuggle people
OL,6,FA further 16 people have been arrested
OL,7,Fby French Police in and around Paris
OL,8,Fin simultaneous raids. 41 migrants
OL,9,Fwere discovered, including 11 who were
OL,10,Fbeing housed in one address.
OL,12,FThe same investigation has already
OL,13,Fseen five other men from the UK
OL,14,Fcharged in February this year.
OL,16,FIt's believed the organised crime
OL,17,Fgroup used commercial airlines from
OL,18,FVietnam to central and eastern Europe
OL,19,Fbefore later moving migrants to the UK
OL,20,Fon small boats and lorries.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
