FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775239864
OL,3,CWoman arrested on suspicion of helping
OL,4,Corganised crime group smuggle people
OL,6,FThe crime group are thought to hold
OL,7,Fthe genuine Vietnamese passports of
OL,8,Fthose smuggled into the UK as debt
OL,9,Fbondage.
OL,11,FSenior Investigating Officer for the
OL,12,FNational Crime Agency, Alex Cruise
OL,13,Fsaid: "Tackling people smuggling
OL,14,Fremains a top priority for the NCA,
OL,15,Fand this is one of approximately 100
OL,16,Fongoing investigations targeting
OL,17,Fgroups or individuals both directly
OL,18,Finvolved in organising journeys, or
OL,19,Fthose who facilitate that criminality."
OL,26,@uD@GOU
